parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or stalls when shifting gears
the transmission slips or jumps out of gear
the engine revs but the vehicle does not move
the vehicle loses power or acceleration
and the "check engine" light comes on intermittently.
